09:26.599 --> 09:29.159
- That's what the guy told me.
- No.

09:29.201 --> 09:31.169
What?

09:31.203 --> 09:34.036
It's currently scheduled for today.

09:34.073 --> 09:35.597
But...

09:35.641 --> 09:37.939
The paper's telling us
that we are due

09:37.977 --> 09:41.378
to do an eviction here
today at 9:00 AM.

09:41.913 --> 09:43.438
Shoot.

09:44.717 --> 09:47.481
Well, he's surprised too.

09:47.520 --> 09:49.681
The house is gone.

09:49.722 --> 09:51.246
That cop told me that the house

09:51.290 --> 09:53.554
has already been sold
to somebody else.

09:53.592 --> 09:56.789
So we don't own the house no more,
somebody else does.

09:58.130 --> 10:01.099
This is capitalism,

10:01.133 --> 10:04.762
a system of taking and giving--

10:04.804 --> 10:07.329
mostly taking.

10:07.373 --> 10:09.273
The only thing we didn't know

10:09.308 --> 10:12.505
was when the revolt would begin.

10:12.545 --> 10:14.706
Everything, we've tried everything...

10:14.747 --> 10:16.374
