10:16.415 --> 10:19.043
I'm thinking about
maybe doing that.

10:19.084 --> 10:22.918
You know, that's one way
somebody could get their money back.

10:22.955 --> 10:25.014
If they did it--
they did it to me,

10:25.057 --> 10:27.526
